 TOM: Bruce is a member of the Edinburgh University Gliding Club and I also need the Loughborough 

00:02:40.790 --> 00:02:43.720
 Thanking University Gliding Club and Alistair who brought me here. 

00:02:43.720 --> 00:02:46.960
 Now back safely to the ground. Thanks again very much. 

